        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Baba Yaga teaches you how to transfer spirits into objects and freeze your foes.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> occult</p>\n<p><strong>Patron Skill</strong> Occultism</p>\n<p><strong>Hex Cantrip</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Spirit Object]</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spell</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Chilling Spray]</p>\n<p><strong>Familiar of Freezing Rime</strong> Your familiar is cold to the touch, its breath always visible. When you Cast or Sustain a hex, you can cause ice to form in a @Template[type:burst|distance:5] centered on a square of your familiar's space. Those squares are difficult terrain until the start of your next turn.</p>\n<p><em>Note: This patron's familiar ability was added per PFS guidelines.</em></p>"
